data.Title: Chair
data.Description: Specical Pattern Design Slipcovers will make your chair brand new and beautiful. A nice decor for your home and your household lives! Polyester covers feature an elastic closure to give a snug fit on the chair.

data.Title: Watch
data.Description: Rolex presents the new generation of its Oyster Perpetual watches and brings a new model to the range, the Oyster Perpetual 41, as well as versions of the Oyster Perpetual 36 displaying dials in vivid colours.

data.Title: Speaker
data.Description: Carry your party with you wherever you go with this JBL Bluetooth speaker. Packed with a number of impressive features, including 10 hours of playback time, a waterproof design and Bluetooth connectivity.

data.Title: Mobile
data.Description: The iPhone X was Apple's flagship 10th anniversary iPhone featuring a 5.8-inch OLED display, facial recognition and 3D camera functionality, a glass body, and an A11 Bionic processor.
